      "term": "nonobservances",
      "kind": "word",
      "cefrLevel": "null",
      "senses": [
        {
          "pos": "noun",
          "definition": "the absence or failure to notice something that should be noticed; lack of observance",
          "examples": [
            "The nonobservances of the warning signs led to the mistaken belief that no danger existed.",
            "Her nonobservances of the rules caused minor clashes within the team."
